[Briefhoofd Richard Green, Fine Paintings, London]. Vraagt mening FG over nieuw verworven werk van Jan Brueghel. Stuurt foto van het werk; [Notitie FG]: '18-3-76: Answered by telephone: There are unsigned pictures by J.B.I but I cannot find a picture by him with the little parallel strokes in the tree foreshore (foreground). So we leave it in the balance whether J.B.I or II.
